{"tid":1254993,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【集中火力】 626、627兵分兩路，對準暴政去打","createTime":"2019-06-24T10:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T01:32:00.000Z","uid":129592,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d50646dc87a29007dac7c2f696023b2a83691baa","tid":1254993,"uid":129592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-24T10:34:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">首先，希望所有不合作運動喺625可以暫停一下。<br />\n625好好回氣，做軟性嘢，打擊不實輿論，做好626文宣工作！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>重申：文宣唔係單靠文宣組，係所有人都要幫手share出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6月26日再次開佢波！</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uct0hEV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuct0hEV.png&h=3f8cde64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xTqaETg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxTqaETg.png&h=9b90bd0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[ 一人一post ] 626 朝早9點到夜晚9點！目標係G20 ! 一定要出！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1254443\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1254443</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">和理非手足們，</span><br />\n626日間係你地嘅回合，加油！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n市民自發行動：626去齊G20領事館請願 <br />\nTelegram: @g20helphk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">勇武手足，</span><br />\n請根據自己呢幾日嘅體力同精神狀況考慮幫拖請願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n626夜晚嘅集會請都盡量出席<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留幾夜就睇風勢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>因為你地嘅最大任務<br />\n係627將行動升級！！！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n但我相信冇人排除到626晚上會點，所以626唔好因為係和理非集會就唔出<im